        "timestamp": "2020-08-07 10:47:12.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nHi,\n\nWouldn't it be valuable to first know why the PR has broken this feature? By creating a test for example? It sounds a bit extreme to revert the whole PR without providing any clear explanation why it caused the problem. \n\nI can definitely help if needed.\n\nThanks,\n\nFrancis.",
