        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2020-08-07 11:07:25.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n(1 comment)\n\nBy looking closely at the change, we can see a a mistake in the code when checking if \"atomic components\" should be added or not (I've added a comment where the change should be done).\n\nHowever, this means that this behavior is not tested anywhere. So here is what we could do:\n- Fix the issue (instead of reverting the code)\n- Write a test to ensure this does not happen again in the past",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
